    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve lived and breathed cars my whole life, and I can honestly say this beauty is one of the cleanest, most preserved examples you\u2019ll ever lay eyes on. She\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with only the finest care; every time I take her out, it feels like stepping into a time capsule. The drive is whisper-smooth and the finish is simply stunning. I\u2019m only looking to find her a new home because I\u2019m starting a new project, and I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who appreciates a truly flawless ride. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so head-over-heels for this car!",
