      "description": "Up for sale is a breathtaking E92 M3, a true final-year masterpiece of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the high-revving S65 V8, delivering linear power delivery all the way to its 8,400 RPM redline. The rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014typical weak points\u2014have been preemptively addressed with upgraded components to ensure bulletproof reliability. The 7-speed DCT shifts with surgical precision, and the EDC-tuned suspension provides a chassis stiffness that remains factory-spec. Every bushing is tight, the VANOS system is silent, and the subframe shows zero signs of fatigue. This is a turn-key, concours-ready machine for the driver who demands mechanical perfection and zero compromise in lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
